:item_3 a guide:SyllabusItem ; guide:itemIndex 3 ; guide:syllabusDescription "Mathematical modelling techniques" .
:item_4 a guide:SyllabusItem ; guide:itemIndex 4 ; guide:syllabusDescription "Compartmental modelling" .
:item_5 a guide:SyllabusItem ; guide:itemIndex 5 ; guide:syllabusDescription "Chronobiological modelling" .
:item_6 a guide:SyllabusItem ; guide:itemIndex 6 ; guide:syllabusDescription "Applications" .

